{
	"name": "Synchronic Combat",
	"type": "spell",
	"img": "icons/magic/defensive/illusion-evasion-echo-purple.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p><em><strong>Target:</strong> One Ally within Range</em></p><p>You and one ally of your choice become mentally linked for up to 1 minute, so long as you can maintain concentration. While linked in this manner, and able to see threats to your ally, you may share saving throws. When either you or your ally is subjected to a saving throw, you both roll and use the higher of the two rolls. This ability does not stack with advantage, but does work with disadvantage.</p><p>In addition, you may grant your ally expertise to one attack as if you had taken the Help action as a reaction. Your ally can similarly use this ability.</p><p>Once you have shared your saving throw, this power ends. This power cannot be used with the Split basic augment.</p><h2>Augments:</h2><p><strong>Castle:</strong> You may instantly change places with your ally so long as they are within 60ft. Doing so ends the power.</p><p><strong>Share Movement:</strong> During your turn while this power is in effect, you may add together your movement and your allyâ€™s movement. When you do so, you may divide that movement in 5ft increments between you and your ally. You must roll your Psi Die for this augment on any turn you wish to use this effect.</p><h2>Augments requiring two Psi Dice</h2><p><strong>Share Attacks:</strong> You may forgo your action to grant your ally an additional action. This ends the power. You must roll your Psi Dice for this augment on any turn you wish to use this effect.</p><p><strong>Unity:</strong> You and your ally share hit points and temporary hit points. Whenever you or your ally takes damage, gains temporary hit points, or receives healing you may expend your reaction to split the value in half and share the loss or gain, rounding up.</p>",
